  "instructions": [
    "Heat the vegetable oil in a wok or large skillet over high heat until it starts to smoke.",
    "Add the minced garlic and grated ginger and stir-fry until they are charred and fragrant.",
    "Add the toffee popcorn and stir-fry for 2 minutes until it is well coated with the garlic and ginger mixture.",
    "Add the soy sauce, rice vinegar, sugar, and cornstarch mixture and stir-fry for 2 minutes until the sauce has thickened.",
    "Add the chopped scallions and roasted peanuts and stir-fry for 1 minute until they are well combined.",
    "Season with salt to taste.",
    "Transfer the Charred Creamy Chinese Toffee Popcorn Kung Pao to a serving platter.",
    "Serve immediately and enjoy."
  ],
